DryadDataFile.dcterms:title: Turtle Dove sequencing data
DryadDataFile.dcterms:description: Single end Illumina reads for the 104 Turlte dove samples used in this study (one sample per file). All reads are 115 bp in length after trimming and removing barcodes as described in the manuscript. Reads with a single base under Phred 10 or more than 5% under Phred 20 were discarded.
